review.reviewBody: Food was good as always, however was packed very poorly and a good portion of the soup spilt into the bag it was in

The fish noodle is pretty good. For the appertizer: chicken wing with butter, i did not feel the butter and did not expect that its very salty, i dont know if Im eating salt or chicken, not recommend this dish.

The Strawberry Smoothie (Sinh To Dau) was abso amazing! The Free-Range Chicken Noodle Soup (Pho Ga) is authentic, the chicken is definitely free range so if you arent into it be aware when ordering. I personally thought it was wonderful and tasted amazing!
Some of the tastiest chicken wings money can buy, my favourite banh mi in the city, and incredibly delicious pho. The people who run this place are the best, I absolutely love this restaurant
order was ready quickly, grilled chicken and prawns were so yummy and I like the strawberry shake too
